title: Ravens rally late, top Steelers 23-20 in overtime
text:
> Sports Ravens rally late, top Steelers 23-20 in overtime Baltimore Ravens kicker Justin Tucker (9) leaves the field after kicking a game-winning field goal in overtime to beat the Pittsburgh Steelers 23-20 in an NFL football game in Pittsburgh, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015. (AP Photo/Gene Puskar)
